{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require disabled toilets on all commercial flights",
        "additional_details": "This is a problem for many people and can put them off travelling. Why should disabled people not be able to travel for something so simple? They shouldn\u2019t be singled out and should be able to access the same facilities as others. This is a huge thing for me and my family as we are big travellers and have family living abroad.",
        "background": "We believe that having a disabled toilets on commercial flights would massively benefit many people.",
